line_1: Into the Head at length She gets,
line_2: And There in Public Grandeur sits,

line_1: Into the Head at length She gets,
line_2: To judge of Things, and censure Wits.

line_1: High-sounding words our worthy Gardener gets,
line_2: And at his club to wondering swains repeats;

line_1: Upon her Back, and on the Crupper gets.
line_2: He minds her not; but up the Boy he sets
